reviewText: These DVDs are so cute, they are claymation and are timeless. They are pretty boring for adults but I think are perfect for maybe 2-5 year olds. I just like the look of it so much.

my kids love these. They are silly and some may not like the humor. But my kids love them 5 & 7 and they are cute and teach life lessons is a fun way. We love that it is the claymation format vs animation. Claymation rocks!
Loved it! A sweet magical world! Very engaging children 3-7.  As always received as told, speedy and in mint condition. Amazon rocks.
